%S A397016 0,4,13,172,11270,3466586,3528858626
%N A397016 Number of undirected self-avoiding cycles in the mod n square grid graph, reduced for symmetry (with rotations, reflections, and translations not counted as distinct).
%C A397016 Here a "mod n square grid graph" is a n X n graph with wrapping allowed, e.g., a path can make a 1 unit step between the left and the right edge (same row) or the top and the bottom edge (same column) of the graph.
%C A397016 Excludes 0 length cycles; including them increases each term by 1.
%e A397016 a(3) = 13:
